description: Demol existing buildings & erect 5 buildings - 1x 6, 2x 12, 1x 18, 1x 24 each with 2 basement levels, for 229 resid flats on upper floors + A1/A2/A3 at basement & ground levels.  Landscaping + access works incl 92 p.s. at Bankside Indl Est, 118-122 Soutwhark St.  New open space incl optional small D1 or D2 class structure to facilitate use of open space at 44 Holland St/ 47 Hopton St.
